Located in {{ill|Ishii Town, Myōdō District|ja|名東郡石井町|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Ōji Shrine (Seiyo, Ehime)|ja|王子神社 (西予市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} – Located in {{ill|Seiyo City|ja|西予市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Ōji Shrine (Saiki, Oita)|ja|王子神社 (佐伯市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} – Located in {{ill|Saiki City|ja|佐伯市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.
