'''Ōji Shrine''' (王子神社, Ōji Jinja) is a {{ill|Shinto shrine|ja|神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shinto shrine|qq=}}.
* {{ill|Ōji Shrine|ja|王子神社 (東京都北区)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōji Shrine|qq=}} (Ōji Gongen) – Located in {{ill|Kita City, Tokyo|ja|北区 (東京都)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kita City, Tokyo|qq=}}. Former {{ill|Gōsha|ja|郷社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gōsha|qq=}}, {{ill|Jun-chokusai Shrine|ja|准勅祭社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jun-chokusai Shrine|qq=}}, and part of the {{ill|Tokyo Ten Shrines|ja|東京十社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokyo Ten Shrines|qq=}}. Associated with {{ill|Wakaichi Ōji|ja|若一王子|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wakaichi Ōji|qq=}}. * {{ill|Ōji Shrine (Midori, Yokohama)|ja|王子神社 (横浜市緑区)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōji Shrine (Midori, Yokohama)|qq=}} – Located in {{ill|Midori Ward, Yokohama|ja|緑区 (横浜市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Midori Ward, Yokohama|qq=}}. * {{ill|Ōji Shrine (Atsugi)|ja|王子神社 (厚木市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōji Shrine (Atsugi)|qq=}} – Located in {{ill|Atsugi, Kanagawa|ja|厚木市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Atsugi, Kanagawa|qq=}} (Ōji, Atsugi). * {{ill|Ōji Shrine (Yamasaki, Kakegawa)|ja|王子神社 (掛川市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōji Shrine (Yamasaki, Kakegawa)|qq=}} – Located in {{ill|Yamasaki, Kakegawa|ja|山崎 (掛川市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamasaki, Kakegawa|qq=}}. Associated with {{ill|Wakaichi Ōji|ja|若一王子|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wakaichi Ōji|qq=}}. * {{ill|Ōji Shrine (Kurama, Kakegawa)|ja|王子神社 (掛川市倉真)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōji Shrine (Kurama, Kakegawa)|qq=}} – Located in {{ill|Kurama, Kakegawa|ja|倉真|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kurama, Kakegawa|qq=}}. * {{ill|Ōji Shrine (Kamiuchida, Kakegawa)|ja|王子神社 (掛川市上内田)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōji Shrine (Kamiuchida, Kakegawa)|qq=}} – Located in {{ill|Kamiuchida, Kakegawa|ja|上内田|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kamiuchida, Kakegawa|qq=}}. * {{ill|Ōji Shrine (Kameoka)|ja|王子神社 (亀岡市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōji Shrine (Kameoka)|qq=}} (Ōji Gongen) – Located in {{ill|Kameoka City|ja|亀岡市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kameoka City|qq=}}, {{ill|Shino Town|ja|篠町|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shino Town|qq=}}, Kameoka. Associated with {{ill|Wakaichi Ōji|ja|若一王子|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wakaichi Ōji|qq=}}. * {{ill|Ōji Shrine (Nada, Kobe)|ja|王子神社 (神戸市灘区)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōji Shrine (Nada, Kobe)|qq=}} – Located in {{ill|Nada Ward, Kobe|ja|灘区 (神戸市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nada Ward, Kobe|qq=}}. * {{ill|Ōji Shrine (Kasai, Hyōgo)|ja|王子神社 (加西市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōji Shrine (Kasai, Hyōgo)|qq=}} – Located in {{ill|Kasai City|ja|加西市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kasai City|qq=}}. * {{ill|Ōji Shrine (Takamatsu)|ja|王子神社 (高松市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōji Shrine (Takamatsu)|qq=}} – Located in {{ill|Takamatsu City|ja|高松市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takamatsu City|qq=}}. * {{ill|Ōji Shrine (Tokushima City)|ja|王子神社 (徳島市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōji Shrine (Tokushima City)|qq=}} – Located in {{ill|Tokushima City|ja|徳島市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokushima City|qq=}}. * {{ill|Ōji Shrine (Ishii, Tokushima)|ja|王子神社 (石井町)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōji Shrine (Ishii, Tokushima)|qq=}} – Located in {{ill|Ishii Town, Myōdō District|ja|名東郡石井町|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ishii Town, Myōdō District|qq=}}. * {{ill|Ōji Shrine (Seiyo, Ehime)|ja|王子神社 (西予市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōji Shrine (Seiyo, Ehime)|qq=}} – Located in {{ill|Seiyo City|ja|西予市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seiyo City|qq=}}. * {{ill|Ōji Shrine (Saiki, Oita)|ja|王子神社 (佐伯市)|qq=draft|qq=d